snippet.title: Hellpoint: The Thespian Feast | Sequel Chapter Launch Trailer | Try it on Steam Now!
snippet.description:
The Thespian Feast presents a free sequel chapter to the story of Hellpoint, an upcoming dark and challenging action RPG blurring the line between science and the occult.
Download it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1243140/Hellpoint_The_Thespian_Feast/

Hellpoint is out on April 16 on PC, PS4, Xbox, Steam
Wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/628670/Hellpoint/

Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/hellpoint 

#hellpoint #Switch #Xbox #PS4 #SoulsLike
